Package org.webcurator.domain.model.core

Interface Summary
Annotatable This interface is implemented by objects that support annotations being attached.
HasDatabaseIdentity Interface for all model objects with a database identity.
HasIdentity Interface for all objects that have temporary identity for the purposes of testing equivalence.
HasOid Interface to allow all database persisted objects to be treated alike.
Lockable An interface for objects that can be locked to enable pessimistic locking.
Overrideable This interface is implemeted by any object that can have profile overrides applied to it.
 

Class Summary
AbstractIdentityObject Abstract base object that provides equivalence testing for database persisted domain objects.
AbstractTarget Base Target object to capture the common behaviour between groups and targets.
AbstractTarget.AccessZone The access zone of the target
AbstractTargetGroupTypeView View of AbstractTarget returning the group type if a group.
Annotation An audited note attached to an object.
ArcHarvestFile This class stores information about an ARC file that forms part of a harvest.
ArcHarvestFileDTO A data transfer object for passing Arc Harvest file data between the components of the Web Curator Tool.
ArcHarvestResource  
ArcHarvestResourceDTO A Data Transfer Oject for ArcHarvestResorce data.
ArcHarvestResult An ARC Harvest Result is the content harvested by a Target Instance, or an altered version of that content created through something like the copy and prune use case.
ArcHarvestResultDTO The Object for transfering harvest result objects between the Asset store and the other web curator components
AuthorisingAgent Represents an Agent responsible for granting permission to harvest a site and provide permission for access.
AuthorisingAgent.AuthorisingAgentComparator This is a comparator to compare two authorisng agents.
BandwidthRestriction The hibernate object for persisting bandwidth restrictions for the WCT.
BusinessObjectFactory The BusinessObjectFactory is responsible for instantiating objects and giving them unique identifiers.
CustomDepositFormCriteriaDTO The data transfer object class used to provide required information to WCT DAS to determine whether or not a custom deposit form is required for the specific submission module.
CustomDepositFormResultDTO The data transfer object class used to receive required information from WCT DAS to determine whether or not a custom deposit form is required for the specific submission module.
DublinCore The DublinCore class contains the basic meta data description fields to be associated with an object.
GroupMember Represents a child/parent relationship between an AbstractTarget and a TargetGroup.
HarvesterStatus The status of a harvest.
HarvestResource A HarvestResource is a resource that has been harvested.
HarvestResourceDTO The Object for transfering Harvest Resources between the web curator components.
HarvestResult The HarvestResult class describes the result of a harvest.
HarvestResultDTO The Object for transfering Harvest Results between the web curator components.
LockSubject Class to create a pessimistic lock on an object.
LogFilePropertiesDTO The Object for transferring Log File Properties between the Asset store and the other web curator components
Notification represents the Notification details in the system.
Permission Represents a Permission.
PermissionExclusion Represents a URL excluded from a permission.
PermissionTemplate Models the permission request template used to generate letters and emails to Authorisation Agents.
Profile The Profile object contains information that enables the user to control how a profile takes place.
ProfileBasicCredentials Profile override credentials for HTTP BASIC authentication.
ProfileCredentials  
ProfileFormCredentials Represents Heritrix form-based credentials.
ProfileOverrides Represents a set of overrides that can be applied to a Heritrix profile.
RejReason A Rejection Reason represents the justification a user specified when setting a Target's status to 'Rejected' or when rejecting a harvested Target Instance.
Schedule A schedule determines how often a Target or TargetGroup will be harvested.
SchedulePattern A SchedulePattern defines a simple pattern that can be used rather than using the Cron Expressions.
Seed Defines a seed that is within the Target.
SeedHistory Defines a seed that was historically used by the Target Instance.
Site Represents a Site object.
Target A Target is a set of seeds, schedules and profile overrides that specify what to harvest, at what times, and what harvest profile to use.
TargetGroup A TargetGroup contains a number of child targets or target groups.
TargetInstance A TargetInstance represents a particular harvest at a given date and time.
TargetInstance.TargetInstanceComparator Internal comparator to allow for sorting the Target Instance objects by state and scheduled date and time.
Task A Task represents an action that must be taken by a user within the WCT system.
UrlPattern Represents a pattern that can identify a site, or portion of a site, to which a Permission record applies.
UrlPattern.UrlComparator Comparator of used to sort UrlPattern objects.
